WEBVTT

00:00.227 --> 00:03.083
Let's learn about what people do every day.

00:06.320 --> 00:08.161
They are brushing their teeth.

00:13.126 --> 00:14.557
He is taking a shower.

00:20.363 --> 00:22.037
He is taking a bath.

00:24.876 --> 00:26.931
She is getting dressed for work.

00:30.152 --> 00:32.419
It's good to wash your hands often.

00:36.251 --> 00:37.979
It's time to have breakfast!

00:42.827 --> 00:45.169
After breakfast, we do the dishes.

00:49.764 --> 00:51.592
She is cleaning the house.

00:57.685 --> 01:00.785
It's time to relax and take a break!

01:06.585 --> 01:09.109
After a long day, we have a drink.

